{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300300/extras/SteamPage_Assemble_Discord.png?t=1736266234\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300300/extras/GROWTH_features.jpg?t=1736266234\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hex grid based soft-strategy puzzle game </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Campaign mode with randomly generated maps puts your problem-solving skills to the test </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cozy and idyllic gameplay  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">8 different animals with unique abilities to expand your toolset for exploring  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Points of Interest reward with additional animals and in some cases even with special ones </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">9 different tile types allow for beautifully crafted maps  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Highly replayable  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300300/extras/Bees.gif?t=1736266234\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Growth</strong> is a cozy, hex grid based soft-strategy game. Explore and populate a procedurally generated world by utilizing the unique abilities of animals. Growth blends the beauty of cozy exploration with challenging navigation around obstacles such as mountains and rivers to populate fertile soil, transforming barren landscapes into lush forests, meadows, and more. Experience an unforgettable mix of discovery and strategy. Start growing your own idyllic landscape! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300300/extras/Animals.gif?t=1736266234\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore and expand an ever-growing, procedurally generated map by cleverly connecting clusters of wildlife. Claim newfound clusters or points of interest to receive additional wildlife or in some cases special rewards. As you expand the landscape you will discover new types of animals, providing unique abilities to overcome obstacles. Whether you're looking for a quick break from work or a relaxed puzzle session, Growths' intuitive gameplay lets you explore a beautiful landscape, tile by tile.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300300/extras/Skilltree.gif?t=1736266234\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Right Off The Bat","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2300300/9031302346c46de4fb02e12fe7031d1b3cedca12.jpg"},{"name":"Bat To The Bones","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2300300/934883dba426a1af55dcde635053e3972bf8dd4c.jpg"},{"name":"A Dam Good Job","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2300300/e1039173bf31a505431bae1a4c36968ba6cb0e52.jpg"},{"name":"Beaver Brothers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2300300/164eaf314b56340e364c3d5d30e665f9906d0b72.jpg"},{"name":"Eagle Eye","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2300300/117785ba412fe234dbfb5e43d7c1fd8080e8c361.jpg"},{"name":"Master Scouter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2300300/45c2a24383c9c49ab04f755546b7088ec8b168a5.jpg"},{"name":"Oink! Oink!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2300300/b9aaa948a5da57583430de474933737598ef232b.jpg"},{"name":"Hogs And Kisses","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2300300/f16931e349ab52ecc727c313ef6d7497db2e254e.jpg"},{"name":"Stampede!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunit